-- Tepco Chairman Katsumata to Announce in March Whether to Quit
-- B y   J o h n   B r i n s l e y
-- 2012-02-15T04:25:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-15/tepco-chairman-katsumata-to-announce-in-march-whether-to-quit.html
Tokyo Electric Power Co. Chairman
 Tsunehisa Katsumata  said he will announce in March whether he
will resign over the Fukushima nuclear crisis. Katsumata was
speaking in the Japanese lower house of parliament.  To contact the reporter on this story:
John Brinsley in Tokyo at 
 jbrinsley@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Aaron Sheldrick at 
 asheldrick@bloomberg.net  